[] = binding conducted to bind from the js class
to the template.  property binding
<h1 [style.color]="titleColor">
get the title class FROM the js class and use it in the template


() =binding conducted to bind from the TEMPLATE to the jsclass.
event binding.
<button (click)="jsClassMEthod($event)">click todo something</button>


[(two way binding)]= binding between the js Class to the template.
binding from the js class to the template. BOTH. two way dataflow.





